latestPosts.caption:
Some stories don’t leave you, they stay hidden in the quiet corners of your mind. Memoire is one such story.
A deeply nostalgic film born from silence, memory, and the ache of what could’ve been.

Starring the incredible @richaa_13 , whose performance brought life to every unspoken emotion. Big hug to my awesome team, it wouldn’t have been possible without you all. 

Eternally grateful to @afdubengale Alliance Française du Bengale and @nicolaslviv for premiering our film in the heart of Kolkata, and to Pocket Films OTT for giving Memoire a home beyond the screen.

As a director, this film is a piece of my heart stitched into fiction. I hope it finds a place in yours too.

Watch now. Remember gently.
